long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Save your favorite website links in one google sheet. This is a quick and easy way to save an article link, video link, membership link, etc.

Have you ever received an email that provided a link to a website, awesome funnel or video but you didn't have time to read or watch it? With URL Tracker, you can save all of those links, rename them so you can easily find them and come back to them later.
